Evaluation/Study Limitations
Different hormones showing different results (James)
Activity data - no females in the study, some participants were more engaged with recording their activity levels
Some CATs are invalid for the hormone data (only 4 valid hormone recorders)
Not all participants had both activity and EDF data.
There were lots of NaNs when merging the activity dataset with the EDF csv due to large time periods where activity was not recorded.

